                    activity,
                    action.site.siteId,
                    action.post.remotePostId.toLong(),
                    ThreadedCommentsActionSource.MY_SITE_COMMENT.sourceDescription
                )
            }
        }
        is PostListAction.DismissPendingNotification -> {
            NativeNotificationsUtils.dismissNotification(action.pushId, activity)
        }
